        "text": "set apart",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "1[189]), i.e. given over to Him as a form of offering, human beings being destroyed, with or without the cattle and spoil as well, according to the gravity of the occasion. For examples, see ",
