        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Here the ‘ban’ is to be put in force against the Israelite who is disloyal to Jehovah. The ban was also a Moabite institution. Mesha in his inscription (see ",
        "children": []
