        "class": "ital",
        "text": "EB.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " s.v. Mesha), ll. 16–18 tells us how, after he had carried off the ‘vessels of Yahweh’ from the town of Nebo (",
